# Fraud Detection & Risk Monitoring Dashboard

## Overview
This project analyzes financial transaction data to identify fraudulent activity,
monitor risk exposure, and support data-driven fraud prevention decisions.

## Business Problem
Financial institutions need visibility into fraudulent transactions across
payment channels, locations, and time periods to reduce financial losses.

## Data Overview
- Transaction amount  
- Payment channel  
- Location  
- Fraud indicator  
- Time (Year / Quarter)  

## Tools Used
- Power BI  
- DAX  
- Excel  

## Analysis Performed
- Fraud rate calculation  
- Channel-level fraud exposure analysis  
- Geographic fraud distribution  
- Time-based trend analysis  

## Key Insights
- Fraud represents a small percentage of transactions but a high financial impact  
- Certain payment channels show higher fraud concentration  
- Fraud activity is concentrated in specific regions  

## Business Value
This dashboard enables risk teams to focus on high-risk channels,
improve fraud monitoring, and reduce financial exposure.

